Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.97,0:03:54.78,body,,0,0,0,,哦 有內涵
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.99,0:03:54.45,body,,0,0,0,,好棒！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.28,0:03:55.69,body,,0,0,0,,好棒！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.11,0:03:57.88,body,,0,0,0,,葵學姐 好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.19,0:03:57.80,body,,0,0,0,,好棒！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.09,0:04:01.05,body,,0,0,0,,那下一個誰還想到了？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.41,0:04:02.28,body,,0,0,0,,那我來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.24,0:04:05.22,body,,0,0,0,,陽菜的新的天文部
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.88,0:04:07.97,body,,0,0,0,,大家都如彗星般出現
